title: Webinar: Dev Superpowers - Xamarin
eventShortDescription:
​During this session we will build an application that runs natively on both Android and iOS.

We will cover:
  • Options for Cross-platform Development
  • Cross-platform Architecture
  • iOS and Android Fundamentals
  • Using Native UI and Controls
